# Reverse proxy + HTTPS for the FastAPI backend (Phase 1). See LAUNCH_PLAN.md §4 / §14.
#
# 1. Replace api.udayalms.com with your real backend subdomain.
# 2. Cloudflare → SSL/TLS → Origin Server → Create Certificate → save the two PEM blocks as
#    ./cf-origin/cert.pem and ./cf-origin/key.pem next to this file.
# 3. Cloudflare → SSL/TLS → set encryption mode to "Full (strict)".
api.udayalms.com {
    tls /etc/caddy/cf-origin/cert.pem /etc/caddy/cf-origin/key.pem
    reverse_proxy api:8001
}
